Title: win_networkadapter: added network adapters to inventory of Windows hosts
Level: 1
Component: inv
Compatible: compat
Edition: cre
Version: 1.4.0b4
Date: 1489665801
Class: feature

The inventory plugin now gathers information on network adapters of Windows hosts. This information is then shown in HW/SW inventory of the host as "Hardware -> Network Adapters."
